.TH "bus_mutex_lock" 9 "bus_mutex_lock" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
bus_mutex_lock \- Acquire the mutex
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "bool" bus_mutex_lock
.BI "(struct mutex *lock "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "lock" 12
w1 bus mutex to acquire
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
It try to acquire the mutex W1_THERM_MAX_TRY times and wait
W1_THERM_RETRY_DELAY between 2 attempts.
.SH "RETURN"
true is mutex is acquired and lock, false otherwise
